social_posts.post_text: Happy Holidays!!!! Enjoy your family during these special days and then join ours in the new year! #ladm
Why Kairos ? Hear the iconic Jackie Sleight and Emmy nominated choreographer Christian Vincent explain the reason they created their program Kairos Pro Dance Prep.
Disney!!!!!!!
My great B day 2023. Grateful :)
LADM Dallas.. Glad to have another year to do what I love . #dance #jazz #ladm #grateful

Favorite moment !!! This has to be one of my favorite moments in all my years teaching on #ladm . On Sunday after the faculty show in Dallas, Jackie announced in her own eloquent and funny fashion that I would ( if all went well) be a Dad on the following Tuesday . The crowd was full of the LADM family as we call it ( teachers, friends, students, kids , fellow faculty members friends of friends , Pro Track, LADM Company). I was literally taken back by the crowd reaction to her announcement . From my perspective , all I felt was a roar of positive energy, love and excitement . I saw company members jumping up and down, my fellow faculty members tearing up and an audience full of arms going up in the air. I was truly humbled and grateful that our LADM family was truly excited to share in the huge step in my family’s journey. Thank you Jackie, LADM faculty, LADM company and family for supporting my growing family . Fallyn Manzella Fukudome-Vincent was born healthy on Tuesday ,February, 14 ….Valentines Day !!!

Check out Christian’s interview with @thejamirsmithshow on all major platforms . We chat about lessons he learned growing up in Canada, being an inspiration for his dance students, and how he is leaving his footprints as an actor. I am proud to be part of the PGEC Committee for the @televisionacad . This illustrious group of choreographers is led by Co-Governors @tessandrachavez and @domkelley . If you are a choreographer , a dancer and or interested in The TV Academy Choreographers Peer group , please follow @choreographyemmys for more information . Personally , being a part of this peer group has been an educational , uplifting and community building experience for me as a dance artist . Find out more for yourself :)

We celebrated him and other great black visionaries . Congrats Patrik!!! He also finally announced that there will be a Noah’s Arc reboot coming out soon ….😉 .. for the fans

Kairos is a program I created with @jackiesleight to help young dancers bridge the gap from the dance convention realm to working in the Professional Commercial dance world . It is primarily about learning some of the practical “need to knows” about Commercial Dance in LA prior to embarking on a career. There is a great deal of learning and also a lot of fun .. Watch some of The Kairos 2023 dancers have some fun in this video :) @kairosprodanceprep @ladancemagic

After filming the video we did a promo tour traveling to #newyork #london #romeitaly and #parisfrance . It was a great time . #madonna #original #originaldancers

It has been some time since I have been in the company of my peers/friends dancing in a rehearsal or on a job. Recently I realized that I miss dancing with my friends. So, I decided to teach an intimate class for a few of us that wanted to speak our language  of dance, together, in a studio again. BTW these dance artists have performed with some of the biggest icons like Prince, Madonna and Britney Spears. They have all continued to evolve and I love them. Thanks Marlyn for letting us use your studio MO Dance and Fitness. #madonnadancers #princedancers #britneyspearsdancers #dance
